high_descs: grab a dirty purple cloth out of the bathtub
walk over to the bathroom sink
wash this purple cloth in the sink and pick it up again
walk over to the bathroom toilet
place the cloth on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: place a clean purple cloth on top of the bathroom toilet

high_descs: Turn around and face the bathtub on your right.
Pick up a rag from the bathtub.
Turn around and walk to the sink on your right.
Clean the rag in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Place the rag on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned rag on top of a toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and face towards the bath tub.
Take the rag that is above the bar of soap.
Turn around and go to the right side sink to the right.
Put the rag in the sink. Turn on then turn off the water. Take the rag out of the sink.
Turn right and go in between the bath tub and toilet, then face the toilet.
Put the rag on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag on a toilet tank.
